Text.SourceString: You’re the new arrival, huh?//Don’t bother me, and I won’t bother you.//<portrait=happy>Ha! <Italic>Sike!</>
Text.LocalizedString: You’re the new arrival, huh?//Don’t bother me, and I won’t bother you.//<portrait=happy>Ha! <Italic>Sike!</>

Text.SourceString: You’re in my way.//No, seriously, you are in my way.
Text.LocalizedString: You’re in my way.//No, seriously, you are in my way.

Text.SourceString: Got business with me?
Text.LocalizedString: Got business with me?

Text.SourceString: I can’t chitchat all day.//Talk to someone else, will you?
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t chitchat all day.//Talk to someone else, will you?

Text.SourceString: The Beach Shack has people in it if you want to chat.
Text.LocalizedString: The Beach Shack has people in it if you want to chat.

Text.SourceString: There’s plenty of room over there if you wanna sit down.
Text.LocalizedString: There’s plenty of room over there if you wanna sit down.

Text.SourceString: You can’t dive from here. You gotta go there.//Go to the inn, then go south. You can dive there.
Text.LocalizedString: You can’t dive from here. You gotta go there.//Go to the inn, then go south. You can dive there.

Text.SourceString: My job’s not just a day at the beach. I have to be on the lookout all the time.//It only takes a split second for somebody to get into trouble in the water.
Text.LocalizedString: My job’s not just a day at the beach. I have to be on the lookout all the time.//It only takes a split second for somebody to get into trouble in the water.

Text.SourceString: And those riptides are no joke!//People think they’re good swimmers, but the waves will pull you under in a split second.
Text.LocalizedString: And those riptides are no joke!//People think they’re good swimmers, but the waves will pull you under in a split second.

Text.SourceString: Didn’t mean to freak you out! It’s calm most of the time. But when a lifeguard tells you to stay close to shore, pay attention.//<portrait=determined>We’re just looking out for you.
Text.LocalizedString: Didn’t mean to freak you out! It’s calm most of the time. But when a lifeguard tells you to stay close to shore, pay attention.//<portrait=determined>We’re just looking out for you.

Text.SourceString: I started lifeguarding in high school and just stuck with it, I guess.//It’s not a hard job, and it helps me stay in shape.
Text.LocalizedString: I started lifeguarding in high school and just stuck with it, I guess.//It’s not a hard job, and it helps me stay in shape.

Text.SourceString: Volleyball – that’s my real passion. Do you play?
Text.LocalizedString: Volleyball – that’s my real passion. Do you play?

Text.SourceString: Join me sometime. We’ll get a game going. Gotta warn you, though. I play to win.
Text.LocalizedString: Join me sometime. We’ll get a game going. Gotta warn you, though. I play to win.

Text.SourceString: It’s cool if it’s not your thing. I won’t hold it against you.//<portrait=determined>I mean, to me, a life without volleyball seems like a pretty sad existence, but I guess you feel the same way about a life without…I dunno…corn?//<portrait=normal>Whatever you grow at your farm.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s cool if it’s not your thing. I won’t hold it against you.//<portrait=determined>I mean, to me, a life without volleyball seems like a pretty sad existence, but I guess you feel the same way about a life without…I dunno…corn?//<portrait=normal>Whatever you grow at your farm.

Text.SourceString: I’m <Italic>starving</>.//Training always makes me hungry.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m <Italic>starving</>.//Training always makes me hungry.

Text.SourceString: Gimme some carbs, you know what I mean? Pizza, pasta, gnocchi…ramen!//<portrait=happy>I would kill for some ramen right now.
Text.LocalizedString: Gimme some carbs, you know what I mean? Pizza, pasta, gnocchi…ramen!//<portrait=happy>I would kill for some ramen right now.

Text.SourceString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!

Text.SourceString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.
Text.LocalizedString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.

Text.SourceString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!

Text.SourceString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.
Text.LocalizedString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.

Text.SourceString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: How about this weather, huh? Rainy one day, sunny the next. Bah!

Text.SourceString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.
Text.LocalizedString: I had no idea what to expect when I woke up this morning.

Text.SourceString: The hot spring is really good for sore muscles. Nothing beats a hot soak after a hard workout.
Text.LocalizedString: The hot spring is really good for sore muscles. Nothing beats a hot soak after a hard workout.

Text.SourceString: Yikes, this rain! I’ve never seen anything like it!
Text.LocalizedString: Yikes, this rain! I’ve never seen anything like it!

Text.SourceString: Yikes, this rain! I’ve never seen anything like it!
Text.LocalizedString: Yikes, this rain! I’ve never seen anything like it!

Text.SourceString: Yikes, this rain! I’ve never seen anything like it!
Text.LocalizedString: Yikes, this rain! I’ve never seen anything like it!

Text.SourceString: Hey, check out my new sneakers! They give me extra spring in my toes. Perfect for volleyball.
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, check out my new sneakers! They give me extra spring in my toes. Perfect for volleyball.

Text.SourceString: I paid way too much for these shoes. Hopefully, they’re going to up my game.
Text.LocalizedString: I paid way too much for these shoes. Hopefully, they’re going to up my game.

Text.SourceString: There’s this pink tree next to the hot spring.//Do you know what it is? Cherry, maybe?
Text.LocalizedString: There’s this pink tree next to the hot spring.//Do you know what it is? Cherry, maybe?

Text.SourceString: It’s pretty, but I’m worried the petals will clog up the drain. <Italic>My</> drain.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s pretty, but I’m worried the petals will clog up the drain. <Italic>My</> drain.

Text.SourceString: Watch out for jellyfish on the beach.//Don’t get stung.
Text.LocalizedString: Watch out for jellyfish on the beach.//Don’t get stung.

Text.SourceString: Oof, the beach is gross today. Smells like dead fish.
Text.LocalizedString: Oof, the beach is gross today. Smells like dead fish.

Text.SourceString: I think it’s just seaweed that washed up, but still. Ugh.
Text.LocalizedString: I think it’s just seaweed that washed up, but still. Ugh.

Text.SourceString: This storm is wild! The beach is going to be a mess tomorrow.//All sorts of trash and debris washes up after weather like this.
Text.LocalizedString: This storm is wild! The beach is going to be a mess tomorrow.//All sorts of trash and debris washes up after weather like this.

Text.SourceString: This storm is wild! The beach is going to be a mess tomorrow.//All sorts of trash and debris washes up after weather like this.
Text.LocalizedString: This storm is wild! The beach is going to be a mess tomorrow.//All sorts of trash and debris washes up after weather like this.

Text.SourceString: This storm is wild! Watch out.
Text.LocalizedString: This storm is wild! Watch out.

Text.SourceString: This storm is wild! Watch out.
Text.LocalizedString: This storm is wild! Watch out.

Text.SourceString: It’s almost the end of the year already. Fast, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: It’s almost the end of the year already. Fast, huh?

Text.SourceString: I might take a class online to learn something new.//Not right now. I’m way too busy. But maybe this Winter, when it’s too cold for volleyball.
Text.LocalizedString: I might take a class online to learn something new.//Not right now. I’m way too busy. But maybe this Winter, when it’s too cold for volleyball.

Text.SourceString: Winter’s almost here.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter’s almost here.

Text.SourceString: I still run to the beach from my house, but the snow slows me down! Bah!//And when it’s icy, forget it. Trying to run on ice is a sure way to break a bone.
Text.LocalizedString: I still run to the beach from my house, but the snow slows me down! Bah!//And when it’s icy, forget it. Trying to run on ice is a sure way to break a bone.

Text.SourceString: The hot spring sounds good right now.//<portrait=annoyed>What is it?
Text.LocalizedString: The hot spring sounds good right now.//<portrait=annoyed>What is it?

Text.SourceString: I’m so itchy today! I’ve got bug bites all over my legs.//The bugs are out in force lately. Great!
Text.LocalizedString: I’m so itchy today! I’ve got bug bites all over my legs.//The bugs are out in force lately. Great!

Text.SourceString: The weather is warming up.//If I dressed any warmer, I’d sweat <Italic>buckets</>.
Text.LocalizedString: The weather is warming up.//If I dressed any warmer, I’d sweat <Italic>buckets</>.

Text.SourceString: It’s Spring, baby! Time to hit the volleyball court and work off my Winter blues!
Text.LocalizedString: It’s Spring, baby! Time to hit the volleyball court and work off my Winter blues!

Text.SourceString: I managed to stay in pretty good shape over Winter, but I feel a little off my game, you know?//<portrait=determined>I’m itching to get in a good workout.
Text.LocalizedString: I managed to stay in pretty good shape over Winter, but I feel a little off my game, you know?//<portrait=determined>I’m itching to get in a good workout.

Text.SourceString: You know the plastic rings six-packs come in?//<portrait=sad>They can kill sea life if they end up in the ocean. It’s so sad.
Text.LocalizedString: You know the plastic rings six-packs come in?//<portrait=sad>They can kill sea life if they end up in the ocean. It’s so sad.

Text.SourceString: Don’t forget to properly dispose of six-pack rings after a picnic. You hear?
Text.LocalizedString: Don’t forget to properly dispose of six-pack rings after a picnic. You hear?

Text.SourceString: I don’t like staying indoors too long, sitting behind a desk. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t like staying indoors too long, sitting behind a desk. Bah!

Text.SourceString: The human body was built to move.
Text.LocalizedString: The human body was built to move.

Text.SourceString: There’s usually an influx of people visiting the beach in Summer.//I get it. Summer, beach. Yeah, whatever.
Text.LocalizedString: There’s usually an influx of people visiting the beach in Summer.//I get it. Summer, beach. Yeah, whatever.

Text.SourceString: I’m seeing more and more people busting out the swimwear.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m seeing more and more people busting out the swimwear.

Text.SourceString: Never buying from White Flamingo again.//Got a new swimsuit, and…
Text.LocalizedString: Never buying from White Flamingo again.//Got a new swimsuit, and…

Text.SourceString: I hadn’t even worn it once!//The first wash, and it shrank. Dang it!
Text.LocalizedString: I hadn’t even worn it once!//The first wash, and it shrank. Dang it!

Text.SourceString: Stargazing is cool.//Didn’t think so at first, but now I’m living at the observatory, I kinda get it.
Text.LocalizedString: Stargazing is cool.//Didn’t think so at first, but now I’m living at the observatory, I kinda get it.

Text.SourceString: You either get it or you don’t.//If you don’t, then it’s your loss.
Text.LocalizedString: You either get it or you don’t.//If you don’t, then it’s your loss.

Text.SourceString: If <NPCName>Zoe’s</> serious about volleyball, I’ll take her under my wing.
Text.LocalizedString: If <NPCName>Zoe’s</> serious about volleyball, I’ll take her under my wing.

Text.SourceString: I was about her age when I started playing. It’s never too early.
Text.LocalizedString: I was about her age when I started playing. It’s never too early.

Text.SourceString: I was gonna get in some volleyball time, but it’s just too wet out there. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: I was gonna get in some volleyball time, but it’s just too wet out there. Bah!

Text.SourceString: Guess I’ll have to stay inside today.
Text.LocalizedString: Guess I’ll have to stay inside today.

Text.SourceString: It really rains the whole day, doesn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: It really rains the whole day, doesn’t it?

Text.SourceString: It really storms the whole day, doesn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: It really storms the whole day, doesn’t it?

Text.SourceString: I was gonna get in some volleyball time, but it’s just too wet out there. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: I was gonna get in some volleyball time, but it’s just too wet out there. Bah!

Text.SourceString: Guess I’ll have to stay inside today.
Text.LocalizedString: Guess I’ll have to stay inside today.

Text.SourceString: It’s gonna snow the whole day today. I just <Italic>know</> it.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s gonna snow the whole day today. I just <Italic>know</> it.

Text.SourceString: Have you seen a pair of sunglasses anywhere?//I lost mine. I’m sure I had them yesterday at work…
Text.LocalizedString: Have you seen a pair of sunglasses anywhere?//I lost mine. I’m sure I had them yesterday at work…

Text.SourceString: Oh <Italic>man</>! I forgot I let <NpcName>Wakuu</> borrow them.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh <Italic>man</>! I forgot I let <NpcName>Wakuu</> borrow them.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Zarah</> was using a metal detector down on the beach the other day, and she found a gold coin.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Zarah</> was using a metal detector down on the beach the other day, and she found a gold coin.

Text.SourceString: You think there might be more?//I should invest in a metal detector.
Text.LocalizedString: You think there might be more?//I should invest in a metal detector.

Text.SourceString: Found a pearl on the beach the other day. Not yours, is it?
Text.LocalizedString: Found a pearl on the beach the other day. Not yours, is it?

Text.SourceString: Sports teach humility. I like that.//Sometimes we win and sometimes we lose.
Text.LocalizedString: Sports teach humility. I like that.//Sometimes we win and sometimes we lose.

Text.SourceString: So what if you lose? Gotta face it and try again tomorrow.//It’s not the end of the world.
Text.LocalizedString: So what if you lose? Gotta face it and try again tomorrow.//It’s not the end of the world.

Text.SourceString: I used to swim a lot when I was a kid, but it didn’t grab me. Not competitive enough, I think.
Text.LocalizedString: I used to swim a lot when I was a kid, but it didn’t grab me. Not competitive enough, I think.

Text.SourceString: I like playing sports where there are winners and losers.
Text.LocalizedString: I like playing sports where there are winners and losers.

Text.SourceString: I jacked up my knee yesterday. I slipped on some leaves and fell down the stairs in front of the bathhouse. Bah!
Text.LocalizedString: I jacked up my knee yesterday. I slipped on some leaves and fell down the stairs in front of the bathhouse. Bah!

Text.SourceString: It kinda hurts when I walk. I guess this is a glimpse into what old age will feel like.
Text.LocalizedString: It kinda hurts when I walk. I guess this is a glimpse into what old age will feel like.

Text.SourceString: Apples are in season, no? Do you have them on your farm, <PlayerName>$Player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Apples are in season, no? Do you have them on your farm, <PlayerName>$Player</>?

Text.SourceString: What’s with the giant chicken they have at the Harvest Festival, huh? So weird!
Text.LocalizedString: What’s with the giant chicken they have at the Harvest Festival, huh? So weird!

Text.SourceString: Where do you think I could get one of those?
Text.LocalizedString: Where do you think I could get one of those?

Text.SourceString: I cleaned the leaves in front of the bathhouse yesterday, and they’re already piling up again.
Text.LocalizedString: I cleaned the leaves in front of the bathhouse yesterday, and they’re already piling up again.

Text.SourceString: Need to find <NpcName>Wakuu</>. It’s his turn to clear the path for <NpcName>Takeba</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Need to find <NpcName>Wakuu</>. It’s his turn to clear the path for <NpcName>Takeba</>.

Text.SourceString: It’s freezing today.//Do a few jumping jacks or push-ups if you wanna get toasty warm. Try it.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s freezing today.//Do a few jumping jacks or push-ups if you wanna get toasty warm. Try it.

Text.SourceString: Is getting mittens worth it, you reckon?//You look like the type who’d have a lot of that kind of thing.
Text.LocalizedString: Is getting mittens worth it, you reckon?//You look like the type who’d have a lot of that kind of thing.

Text.SourceString: I’ll see if <NpcName>Wakuu</> has some and test-drive them, maybe.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ll see if <NpcName>Wakuu</> has some and test-drive them, maybe.

Text.SourceString: Dry air…bah!//What is it?
Text.LocalizedString: Dry air…bah!//What is it?

Text.SourceString: One of those giant animal suits from White Flamingo would be nice.//<portrait=determined>Nice and toasty inside.
Text.LocalizedString: One of those giant animal suits from White Flamingo would be nice.//<portrait=determined>Nice and toasty inside.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Wakuu</> goes to see his dad every weekend like clockwork.//Come Saturday, the place is all mine until Monday.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Wakuu</> goes to see his dad every weekend like clockwork.//Come Saturday, the place is all mine until Monday.

Text.SourceString: I know <NpcName>Wataru</> gardens at his house. Has a small patch in front of the lighthouse.//<NpcName>Wakuu</> always brings random produce back to the observatory. Tastes great! Really fresh.//<portrait=concerned>What do they do now Winter is here? Can’t be gardening, can it?
Text.LocalizedString: I know <NpcName>Wataru</> gardens at his house. Has a small patch in front of the lighthouse.//<NpcName>Wakuu</> always brings random produce back to the observatory. Tastes great! Really fresh.//<portrait=concerned>What do they do now Winter is here? Can’t be gardening, can it?

Text.SourceString: Are you doing one of those New Year’s resolution things?//<portrait=determined>Mine is the same every year. Get better at life.
Text.LocalizedString: Are you doing one of those New Year’s resolution things?//<portrait=determined>Mine is the same every year. Get better at life.

Text.SourceString: I started lifeguarding during my last Summer of high school, before I moved to Coral Island.//<portrait=happy>I didn’t think I’d still be doing it all these years later, but no complaints.
Text.LocalizedString: I started lifeguarding during my last Summer of high school, before I moved to Coral Island.//<portrait=happy>I didn’t think I’d still be doing it all these years later, but no complaints.

Text.SourceString: I only work the afternoon shift, so I have lots of time to practice volleyball.//<portrait=determined>Gotta keep my eyes on the prize, you know what I mean?
Text.LocalizedString: I only work the afternoon shift, so I have lots of time to practice volleyball.//<portrait=determined>Gotta keep my eyes on the prize, you know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: I’ve been swimming for years, but you know what I wish I did more of? Diving.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve been swimming for years, but you know what I wish I did more of? Diving.

Text.SourceString: Maybe I could train to be a deep-sea diver. Who knows?
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I could train to be a deep-sea diver. Who knows?

Text.SourceString: You know the Hillside observatory? I live out there.
Text.LocalizedString: You know the Hillside observatory? I live out there.

Text.SourceString: Kind of a hike to get to the beach, but I like that. Keeps me in shape, you know?
Text.LocalizedString: Kind of a hike to get to the beach, but I like that. Keeps me in shape, you know?

Text.SourceString: Up for a game?
Text.LocalizedString: Up for a game?

Text.SourceString: Might stop by the Beach Shack later, pick up some coconuts.//I’m kinda in the mood for one.
Text.LocalizedString: Might stop by the Beach Shack later, pick up some coconuts.//I’m kinda in the mood for one.

Text.SourceString: I like playing volleyball with <NPCName>Aaliyah</>.//We both play hard, you know what I mean?
Text.LocalizedString: I like playing volleyball with <NPCName>Aaliyah</>.//We both play hard, you know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: Have you seen that dog running around town? <NPCName>Taco</>?//<portrait=happy>I love that scruffy guy.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you seen that dog running around town? <NPCName>Taco</>?//<portrait=happy>I love that scruffy guy.

Text.SourceString: This one time, I saw <NPCName>Taco</> swimming in the fountain. Yeah, the one in front of the general store.//<portrait=happy>What a funny little dude.
Text.LocalizedString: This one time, I saw <NPCName>Taco</> swimming in the fountain. Yeah, the one in front of the general store.//<portrait=happy>What a funny little dude.

Text.SourceString: I’ve thought about getting a pet, but between volleyball practice and workouts and work, I’m hardly ever home to take care of one.//<portrait=concerned>I don’t want to stay cooped up in my house like <NpcName>Wakuu</>, and that’s not fair to a pet.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve thought about getting a pet, but between volleyball practice and workouts and work, I’m hardly ever home to take care of one.//<portrait=concerned>I don’t want to stay cooped up in my house like <NpcName>Wakuu</>, and that’s not fair to a pet.

Text.SourceString: Unless I brought them out with me. I hadn’t thought about that.
Text.LocalizedString: Unless I brought them out with me. I hadn’t thought about that.

Text.SourceString: Who made that sign for the Beach Shack?//<portrait=annoyed>The coconut drink sign says Buy Two, Get Two. It’s funny ’cause it reminds me of something my dad always said.
Text.LocalizedString: Who made that sign for the Beach Shack?//<portrait=annoyed>The coconut drink sign says Buy Two, Get Two. It’s funny ’cause it reminds me of something my dad always said.

Text.SourceString: Are you here to eat, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you here to eat, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Frank’s</> pesto pasta is good.//<portrait=happy>Easy to overeat.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Frank’s</> pesto pasta is good.//<portrait=happy>Easy to overeat.

Text.SourceString: I hate to think about getting older.//<portrait=determined>I’m in the prime of my life, <PlayerName>$player</>. I’m in better shape now than I’ve ever been.
Text.LocalizedString: I hate to think about getting older.//<portrait=determined>I’m in the prime of my life, <PlayerName>$player</>. I’m in better shape now than I’ve ever been.

Text.SourceString: But it doesn’t last forever, you know?//You don’t see grandparents competing in the Pokyo Volleyball Tournament.
Text.LocalizedString: But it doesn’t last forever, you know?//You don’t see grandparents competing in the Pokyo Volleyball Tournament.

Text.SourceString: I feel dizzy… My head…//Whoaaaaa… I might’ve caught something.
Text.LocalizedString: I feel dizzy… My head…//Whoaaaaa… I might’ve caught something.

Text.SourceString: Hmm… Should I get my flu shot now? Kinda don’t wanna go to the clinic.//Not a fan of clinics or hospitals. That’s where <Italic>sick</> people go, you know what I mean?
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm… Should I get my flu shot now? Kinda don’t wanna go to the clinic.//Not a fan of clinics or hospitals. That’s where <Italic>sick</> people go, you know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: I’m sure the one in town is cleaner than my room right now, but who knows what kind of germs or viruses are in there? *shivers*
Text.LocalizedString: I’m sure the one in town is cleaner than my room right now, but who knows what kind of germs or viruses are in there? *shivers*

Text.SourceString: I’m not in the mood.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m not in the mood.

Text.SourceString: I live up the hill ’cause it’s a killer workout every day. And the view from the observatory tower? It’s insane!//You been up there? Yeah, you know what’s up.
Text.LocalizedString: I live up the hill ’cause it’s a killer workout every day. And the view from the observatory tower? It’s insane!//You been up there? Yeah, you know what’s up.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Wakuu</> and I have completely different schedules, so we don’t get in each other’s way. It’s perfect.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Wakuu</> and I have completely different schedules, so we don’t get in each other’s way. It’s perfect.

Text.SourceString: I’m gonna have to skip the beach today.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m gonna have to skip the beach today.

Text.SourceString: I can’t believe how much weight I’ve been able to lift lately.//I’m really sore, though.
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t believe how much weight I’ve been able to lift lately.//I’m really sore, though.

Text.SourceString: Dang, I forgot my water bottle again. I swear, my mind’s in the clouds today.//<portrait=annoyed>At least I still have my head on my shoulders, or I’d probably lose it too!
Text.LocalizedString: Dang, I forgot my water bottle again. I swear, my mind’s in the clouds today.//<portrait=annoyed>At least I still have my head on my shoulders, or I’d probably lose it too!

Text.SourceString: I think I pulled a muscle in my leg during practice the other day.//I’m going to have to sit out for a little while.
Text.LocalizedString: I think I pulled a muscle in my leg during practice the other day.//I’m going to have to sit out for a little while.

Text.SourceString: I’m hyped for the Cherry Blossom Festival next week. The food is always next level.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m hyped for the Cherry Blossom Festival next week. The food is always next level.

Text.SourceString: I gotta clean my place next week. It’s a total disaster.//<portrait=concerned>Also, I’m missing a pair of shorts.
Text.LocalizedString: I gotta clean my place next week. It’s a total disaster.//<portrait=concerned>Also, I’m missing a pair of shorts.

Text.SourceString: This year is zooming by <Italic>fast</>!//It feels like we just celebrated New Year’s yesterday.
Text.LocalizedString: This year is zooming by <Italic>fast</>!//It feels like we just celebrated New Year’s yesterday.

Text.SourceString: I’m thinking of getting a tat. I want something that screams strength and perseverance. Cool, huh?//<portrait=annoyed>But honestly, between you and me, I’m a bit of a wimp when it comes to needles. What if it’s not sterile or something?
Text.LocalizedString: I’m thinking of getting a tat. I want something that screams strength and perseverance. Cool, huh?//<portrait=annoyed>But honestly, between you and me, I’m a bit of a wimp when it comes to needles. What if it’s not sterile or something?

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Aaliyah</> can throw stones so far out into the sea. I need to ask her to teach me how to do it.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Aaliyah</> can throw stones so far out into the sea. I need to ask her to teach me how to do it.

Text.SourceString: Dang, your smile is killer!
Text.LocalizedString: Dang, your smile is killer!

Text.SourceString: It’s infectious. I can’t help but smile when I’m around you.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s infectious. I can’t help but smile when I’m around you.

Text.SourceString: I don’t want to come on too strong, but I just have to say it. You are one fine specimen of a human being.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t want to come on too strong, but I just have to say it. You are one fine specimen of a human being.

Text.SourceString: You know, I think you and I would make a pretty great team.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, I think you and I would make a pretty great team.

Text.SourceString: You have such a unique style. I love it.
Text.LocalizedString: You have such a unique style. I love it.

Text.SourceString: You always seem to know the right thing to say. I admire that about you.
Text.LocalizedString: You always seem to know the right thing to say. I admire that about you.

Text.SourceString: You’re a really great listener. I always feel heard and understood when I talk to you.
Text.LocalizedString: You’re a really great listener. I always feel heard and understood when I talk to you.

Text.SourceString: Winter makes me appreciate the warmer weather even more.//Bring on the Summer sun, baby!
Text.LocalizedString: Winter makes me appreciate the warmer weather even more.//Bring on the Summer sun, baby!

Text.SourceString: I always feel like a real adult when I shovel snow.//<portrait=happy>Like, look at me being a responsible homeowner and stuff.
Text.LocalizedString: I always feel like a real adult when I shovel snow.//<portrait=happy>Like, look at me being a responsible homeowner and stuff.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Takeba</> takes great care of the bathhouse. We should go there sometime…together.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Takeba</> takes great care of the bathhouse. We should go there sometime…together.

Text.SourceString: Having short hair is awesome for beach volleyball.//Sand just slides right off. No fuss, no muss.
Text.LocalizedString: Having short hair is awesome for beach volleyball.//Sand just slides right off. No fuss, no muss.

Text.SourceString: I offered <NpcName>Alice</> some pizza when we were at the beach the other day, but she said it makes her bloated.//<portrait=happy>Oh well. More for me, I guess!
Text.LocalizedString: I offered <NpcName>Alice</> some pizza when we were at the beach the other day, but she said it makes her bloated.//<portrait=happy>Oh well. More for me, I guess!

Text.SourceString: She also said it was nasty. What <Italic>is</> her problem?
Text.LocalizedString: She also said it was nasty. What <Italic>is</> her problem?

Text.SourceString: Ugh, hate fish. It’s the one thing I just can’t stomach.//Something about the taste and texture just makes me want to gag.
Text.LocalizedString: Ugh, hate fish. It’s the one thing I just can’t stomach.//Something about the taste and texture just makes me want to gag.

Text.SourceString: Smoked, though. Fish tastes kinda good when you smoke it.
Text.LocalizedString: Smoked, though. Fish tastes kinda good when you smoke it.

Text.SourceString: <Italic>Man</>, I’m craving some ramen.//<portrait=determined>I’m not too fussy when it comes to food, though. I’ll take any ramen. Seafood ramen, veggie ramen – whatever!
Text.LocalizedString: <Italic>Man</>, I’m craving some ramen.//<portrait=determined>I’m not too fussy when it comes to food, though. I’ll take any ramen. Seafood ramen, veggie ramen – whatever!

Text.SourceString: <Italic>Man</>, shoveling snow is such a workout. My arms are gonna be sore tomorrow.
Text.LocalizedString: <Italic>Man</>, shoveling snow is such a workout. My arms are gonna be sore tomorrow.

Text.SourceString: I don’t keep my dumbbells in my room because I’m selfish or anything.//<portrait=surprised>It’s just that sometimes I like to work out early in the morning when <NpcName>Wakuu</> is still asleep.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t keep my dumbbells in my room because I’m selfish or anything.//<portrait=surprised>It’s just that sometimes I like to work out early in the morning when <NpcName>Wakuu</> is still asleep.

Text.SourceString: I don’t want to disturb his rest, you know? I’m just being considerate.//<portrait=blushing>I’m nice, huh? I bet that’s why you like me. *winks* Ha ha!
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t want to disturb his rest, you know? I’m just being considerate.//<portrait=blushing>I’m nice, huh? I bet that’s why you like me. *winks* Ha ha!

Text.SourceString: These icy sidewalks give me anxiety, I swear. I’m so afraid of slipping and falling!//Can’t take any chances when I only have two legs.
Text.LocalizedString: These icy sidewalks give me anxiety, I swear. I’m so afraid of slipping and falling!//Can’t take any chances when I only have two legs.

Text.SourceString: Please, <NPCName>Goddess</>, keep me safe out there.
Text.LocalizedString: Please, <NPCName>Goddess</>, keep me safe out there.

Text.SourceString: When <NpcName>Wakuu</> brings home his catch from the weekend, it stinks up the whole dang house. Drives me nuts!
Text.LocalizedString: When <NpcName>Wakuu</> brings home his catch from the weekend, it stinks up the whole dang house. Drives me nuts!

Text.SourceString: Can’t wait for Summer to roll around again! The beach, the sun, the sand. It’s my favorite season.
Text.LocalizedString: Can’t wait for Summer to roll around again! The beach, the sun, the sand. It’s my favorite season.

Text.SourceString: Have you ever wondered where <NpcName>Wakuu</> gets his money?//The dude’s always splurging on fancy coffee <Italic>every day</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you ever wondered where <NpcName>Wakuu</> gets his money?//The dude’s always splurging on fancy coffee <Italic>every day</>.

Text.SourceString: Do scientists really rake in that much cash?
Text.LocalizedString: Do scientists really rake in that much cash?

Text.SourceString: The observatory gets super chilly in Winter. I swear it’s because of the size.//The place is way too big.
Text.LocalizedString: The observatory gets super chilly in Winter. I swear it’s because of the size.//The place is way too big.

Text.SourceString: I have no clue who decked out the observatory. It was already looking fresh when I rolled in.
Text.LocalizedString: I have no clue who decked out the observatory. It was already looking fresh when I rolled in.

Text.SourceString: Must’ve been the boss man, <NpcName>Wakuu</>, who did the magic.//<portrait=normal>Swimming in cash, that dude.
Text.LocalizedString: Must’ve been the boss man, <NpcName>Wakuu</>, who did the magic.//<portrait=normal>Swimming in cash, that dude.

Text.SourceString: Who else could it have been, a ghost? Ha ha ha!//<portrait=concerned>No, seriously. Don’t joke about ghosts. It freaks me out.
Text.LocalizedString: Who else could it have been, a ghost? Ha ha ha!//<portrait=concerned>No, seriously. Don’t joke about ghosts. It freaks me out.

Text.SourceString: You know those charms that’re supposed to keep bad spirits away?//<portrait=annoyed>It might sound goofy, but I have one in my room all the time, just in case.
Text.LocalizedString: You know those charms that’re supposed to keep bad spirits away?//<portrait=annoyed>It might sound goofy, but I have one in my room all the time, just in case.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Ben</> hooked me up with it, so like, who knows if it’s legit, right?
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Ben</> hooked me up with it, so like, who knows if it’s legit, right?

Text.SourceString: So, like, I was walkin’ home late one night, right? And I swear, I saw this ghost by the observatory!//<portrait=concerned>It was short, sorta cylinder-shaped, and it moved super fast. <Italic>Man</>, I couldn’t sleep for days after that!
Text.LocalizedString: So, like, I was walkin’ home late one night, right? And I swear, I saw this ghost by the observatory!//<portrait=concerned>It was short, sorta cylinder-shaped, and it moved super fast. <Italic>Man</>, I couldn’t sleep for days after that!

Text.SourceString: I mean, it might’ve been <NpcName>Archie</> or <NPCName>Taco</>, but at 9 pm?//<portrait=concerned>Nah, I’m pretty sure it was a ghost, for real.
Text.LocalizedString: I mean, it might’ve been <NpcName>Archie</> or <NPCName>Taco</>, but at 9 pm?//<portrait=concerned>Nah, I’m pretty sure it was a ghost, for real.

Text.SourceString: Oh, the observatory is <Italic>totally</> haunted, no doubt.//I don’t have any solid proof or anything, but my gut just tells me it’s true.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, the observatory is <Italic>totally</> haunted, no doubt.//I don’t have any solid proof or anything, but my gut just tells me it’s true.

Text.SourceString: You know, some scientists actually believe in ghosts.//<portrait=surprised>Like <NPCName>Scott</>. He’s some kind of scientist, and he told me there’s something sketchy goin’ on at that beach villa.//<portrait=concerned>Yeah, you won’t see me anywhere near that place.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, some scientists actually believe in ghosts.//<portrait=surprised>Like <NPCName>Scott</>. He’s some kind of scientist, and he told me there’s something sketchy goin’ on at that beach villa.//<portrait=concerned>Yeah, you won’t see me anywhere near that place.

Text.SourceString: He also mentioned that basil might help with getting rid of bad spirits, so maybe he’s not <Italic>totally</> on point.
Text.LocalizedString: He also mentioned that basil might help with getting rid of bad spirits, so maybe he’s not <Italic>totally</> on point.

Text.SourceString: I kinda wish you were heading home with me tonight.//It’d be nice to have some company.
Text.LocalizedString: I kinda wish you were heading home with me tonight.//It’d be nice to have some company.

Text.SourceString: It’s always a good idea to swim with a buddy or stay close to the lifeguard tower.//I’m here to help if anything goes wrong. It’s better to be safe than sorry.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s always a good idea to swim with a buddy or stay close to the lifeguard tower.//I’m here to help if anything goes wrong. It’s better to be safe than sorry.

Text.SourceString: If you start feelin’ dizzy, head to the Beach Shack and grab a drink.
Text.LocalizedString: If you start feelin’ dizzy, head to the Beach Shack and grab a drink.

Text.SourceString: Chill in the shade and avoid that direct sun.//<portrait=sad>I don’t want you gettin’ heatstroke or anything.
Text.LocalizedString: Chill in the shade and avoid that direct sun.//<portrait=sad>I don’t want you gettin’ heatstroke or anything.

Text.SourceString: The sunset at the beach is just unreal.//Stick around and watch it with me.
Text.LocalizedString: The sunset at the beach is just unreal.//Stick around and watch it with me.

Text.SourceString: I’ve been working on my serve lately. It’s all about that perfect balance of power and control, you know what I mean?
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve been working on my serve lately. It’s all about that perfect balance of power and control, you know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: After a long day at work or practice, I like to unwind with a big bowl of ramen.//<portrait=happy>The spicier, the better!
Text.LocalizedString: After a long day at work or practice, I like to unwind with a big bowl of ramen.//<portrait=happy>The spicier, the better!

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Aaliyah’s</> got this cool plane sweater, huh? I wonder if they make one with a duck or somethin’.//<portrait=determined>I’d totally rock that.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Aaliyah’s</> got this cool plane sweater, huh? I wonder if they make one with a duck or somethin’.//<portrait=determined>I’d totally rock that.

Text.SourceString: You should come join me for a workout sometime!//I could show you some of my favorite exercises, and we could keep each other motivated.
Text.LocalizedString: You should come join me for a workout sometime!//I could show you some of my favorite exercises, and we could keep each other motivated.

Text.SourceString: I tried making green pesto pasta the other night, and it was super delish!//<portrait=happy>I’m thinkin’ I’ll make it again tomorrow, maybe add some extra veggies.
Text.LocalizedString: I tried making green pesto pasta the other night, and it was super delish!//<portrait=happy>I’m thinkin’ I’ll make it again tomorrow, maybe add some extra veggies.

Text.SourceString: I usually just buy it from the Tavern, but money’s a little tight lately.//<portrait=happy>Or I could always eat <NpcName>Wakuu’s</> food again. Ha ha! Kidding, <PlayerName>$Player</>!//Live a little!
Text.LocalizedString: I usually just buy it from the Tavern, but money’s a little tight lately.//<portrait=happy>Or I could always eat <NpcName>Wakuu’s</> food again. Ha ha! Kidding, <PlayerName>$Player</>!//Live a little!

Text.SourceString: Yesterday morning, I did my workout at the beach, and <Italic>man</>, the sand really made things more challenging.//<portrait=determined>But hey, I got to dive right into the ocean after, so it was a pretty sweet way to start the day!
Text.LocalizedString: Yesterday morning, I did my workout at the beach, and <Italic>man</>, the sand really made things more challenging.//<portrait=determined>But hey, I got to dive right into the ocean after, so it was a pretty sweet way to start the day!

Text.SourceString: You won’t believe the dream I had last night.//<portrait=happy>I was an astronaut, exploring the farthest reaches of the galaxy. It was so surreal!
Text.LocalizedString: You won’t believe the dream I had last night.//<portrait=happy>I was an astronaut, exploring the farthest reaches of the galaxy. It was so surreal!

Text.SourceString: <Italic>Man</>! I’ve been hanging out too much with the space geeks.
Text.LocalizedString: <Italic>Man</>! I’ve been hanging out too much with the space geeks.

Text.SourceString: What do you think I should grab from the menu?
Text.LocalizedString: What do you think I should grab from the menu?

Text.SourceString: You gotta try <NpcName>Frank’s</> basil pesto pasta. It’s the <Italic>bomb</>!
Text.LocalizedString: You gotta try <NpcName>Frank’s</> basil pesto pasta. It’s the <Italic>bomb</>!

Text.SourceString: I’m loving the Tavern’s playlist.//<portrait=happy>They’ve got a perfect mix of classic hits and fresh tunes. Makes me wanna bop.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m loving the Tavern’s playlist.//<portrait=happy>They’ve got a perfect mix of classic hits and fresh tunes. Makes me wanna bop.

Text.SourceString: Where do you think they get this wine from? Your farm or something?//<portrait=blushing>’Cause it’s seriously tasty! *hic*
Text.LocalizedString: Where do you think they get this wine from? Your farm or something?//<portrait=blushing>’Cause it’s seriously tasty! *hic*

Text.SourceString: Have a seat. Let’s chill out a little!
Text.LocalizedString: Have a seat. Let’s chill out a little!

Text.SourceString: One…two…one…two…
Text.LocalizedString: One…two…one…two…

Text.SourceString: Wanna join me for a workout?
Text.LocalizedString: Wanna join me for a workout?

Text.SourceString: Heading to the hot spring? It’s that way, behind this building.
Text.LocalizedString: Heading to the hot spring? It’s that way, behind this building.

Text.SourceString: Need to eat more bananas, for sure.//Don’t want any cramps after all this!
Text.LocalizedString: Need to eat more bananas, for sure.//Don’t want any cramps after all this!

Text.SourceString: The weather is nice today.//Outdoor time, baby!
Text.LocalizedString: The weather is nice today.//Outdoor time, baby!

Text.SourceString: Took me forever to put these pants on. Do they really have to be this tight?
Text.LocalizedString: Took me forever to put these pants on. Do they really have to be this tight?

Text.SourceString: Where are my sweatpants anyway?//I keep misplacing stuff. Bleh.
Text.LocalizedString: Where are my sweatpants anyway?//I keep misplacing stuff. Bleh.
